						<summary>

						<p>This records a gift of land at Nallaraiśūr and 45 kalam of paddy (in place of money ?) by Rājasundari a <hi rend="italic">dēvaraḍiyāḷ</hi> of the temple of Tāntōṉṟi-Mahādēvar at Vīrarājēndrapuram (Jambai) to provide for offerings to god Ūruḍaiya-Paramēśvara during the early morning service.</p>						

